Rzeczowniki policzalne i niepoliczalne można poprzedać określeniami ilości takimi jak:
a jar, bottle, piece, loaf, cup, bar, glass, kilo, carton, bowl, can, jug, slice, tin, packet + of.
a jar of marmalade
a bottle of beer
a loaf of bread
a glass of milk
a cup of coffee
a kilo of meat
a piece of pie
a bar of chocolate
a carton of milk
a bowl of soup
a can of fruit juice
a jug of orange juice
a slice of bread
a tin of fish
a packet of spaghetti

